## Benchmarks

Hardware:
1. Arm tests were run on an Orange Pi Zero 3 with a Cortex-A53 processor.
2. x64 tests were run on a laptop with an Intel i7-7700HQ processor.
3. T4 tests were run in Google Colab on Nvidia T4

